get init :  to create a reporsitory from the curent folder
git status:  get the status of the repository
git commit -m "message": all staged changes will be committed/saved. the "message" helps to documment the changes
git diff
git checkout
git branch :  get all branchs in the repository
git branch "branch_name": the create a branch named branch_name from the curent branch/master

 